The paper proposes a system for automated essay grading using ontologies and textual entailment. This involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques, which are commonly associated with the arXiv CS sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of ontologies also suggests a potential fit with the information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybernetics (cs.CY) sub-categories.
